---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Kindred"
  description="Kindred is a UK adult dating site built on niche-first matching, consent, and real conversation. Learn who we are and why we built it."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 720px;">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>A dating site for people who know what they want.</h1>
      <p>
        Most dating apps flatten everyone into the same template. Kindred doesn't.
        We built a community where your actual interests &mdash; the specific
        stuff you care about &mdash; are the first filter, not an afterthought.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're a small UK team. Our rules are simple: consent first, verified
        profiles only, zero tolerance for shaming, and no ads selling your data.
        We're paid by members who want the full feature set &mdash; that's it.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 48px;">What we believe</h2>
      <ul class="clean benefits" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <li><strong>Consent is non-negotiable</strong>Every feature is designed around giving members control over who sees what, and when.</li>
        <li><strong>Niche-first matching works</strong>You match better when you're honest about what you're into. We make that easy and safe.</li>
        <li><strong>Local communities matter</strong>Long-distance matches are fun, but real life happens in your city.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 48px;">18+ only</h2>
      <p>
        Kindred is strictly for adults. Every profile is verified. If you're
        under 18, this site isn't for you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
